# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your own values.
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# These are Vite build-time variables: they are read when you run
# `npm run dev` / `npm run build` and inlined into the client bundle.
# The Supabase "publishable" (anon) key is safe to expose in the browser —
# it is already shipped in the public production bundle.

